---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Neighborhood Map
metaDescription: A map of the neighborhoods that make up White Plains, New York.
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">White Plains</p>
    <h1>Neighborhood map</h1>
    <p>A simple map of the neighborhoods that make up White Plains. Use it as a starting point for getting oriented to the city.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <figure
      class="about-photo map-figure neighborhood-map-figure"
      id="wpcna-map"
    >
      <img
        src="{{ featuredNeighborhoodMap.imagePath | withPrefix }}?v={{ featuredNeighborhoodMap.imageVersion }}"
        alt="{{ featuredNeighborhoodMap.imageAlt }}"
        loading="eager"
        class="neighborhood-map-image"
      >
      <svg
        class="map-outline-svg"
        viewBox="0 0 {{ featuredNeighborhoodMap.viewBoxWidth }} {{ featuredNeighborhoodMap.viewBoxHeight }}"
        aria-hidden="true"
        focusable="false"
        preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"
      >
        {% for region in featuredNeighborhoodMap.allRegions %}
          <path class="map-outline-path" data-map-outline="{{ region.slug }}" d="{{ region.pathD }}"></path>
        {% endfor %}
      </svg>
      <figcaption id="wpcna-map-caption" class="interactive-map-caption neighborhood-map-caption">
        Map of White Plains neighborhoods.
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <div class="spotlight neighborhood-map-spotlight">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Explore</p>
        <h2>Browse the neighborhoods</h2>
        <p>WPCNA tracks every named neighborhood across White Plains, from Downtown to the hills on the city's edge. Each one has its own page with photos, history, and what makes it distinct.</p>
        <p class="resource-action-stack"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="{{ '/neighborhoods/' | withPrefix }}">All neighborhoods</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="spotlight-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h3>Why neighborhoods matter</h3>
        <p>Each neighborhood has its own character, concerns, and priorities. WPCNA exists to help those neighborhoods stay connected to each other and to the city.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-outline btn-block resource-card-action" href="{{ '/about/' | withPrefix }}">About WPCNA</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<script>
(function () {
  var fig = document.getElementById('wpcna-map');
  var cap = document.getElementById('wpcna-map-caption');
  if (!fig) return;

  var params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
  var slug = params.get('highlight');
  var hash = (window.location.hash || '').replace('#', '');
  if (!slug && hash) slug = hash;
  if (!slug) return;
  var outline = fig.querySelector('[data-map-outline="' + slug + '"]');
  if (!outline) return;

  outline.classList.add('is-active');

  var name = slug.replace(/-/g, ' ').replace(/\b\w/g, function (c) { return c.toUpperCase(); });
  if (cap) cap.textContent = 'Outlined: ' + name;

  requestAnimationFrame(function () {
    fig.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
  });
})();
</script>
